The '''Chief of Property Resources''' was a rank within the hierarchy of the [[Commerce Guild/Legends|Commerce Guild]]. [[Shu Mai/Legends|Shu Mai]] once held this rank for some time before eventually becoming the Guild's [[Presidente/Legends|Presidente]].

